Package: supreme
Title: Structure your Shiny application developed with modules
Description: supreme helps you structure your Shiny application developed with 
    modules. Possible to 1. model and visualize your existing application or design 
    a new one from scratch; 2. keep track of your modules that are either placed 
    in the different parts or reused in multiple places in your existing 
    application.
